      "A swarm consisting of six Lesser Forest Slimes and two Level 4 Mangy Coyotes pursued Artie.",
      "Artie narrowly escaped a coyote attack, triggering a 'Near-Miss' system warning.",
      "Artie crossed the shimmering energy boundary into the Oakhaven Outskirts.",
      "The Aggro Aura was suppressed by regional restrictions upon entering the Outskirts."
    ],
